build a WalT image using a Dockerfile

Usage:
    walt image build --from-url <git-repo-url> [--sub-dir <path>] <image-name>
    walt image build --from-dir <local-directory> <image-name>

    See 'walt help show image-build' for more info.
    
Meta-switches:
    -h, --help                    Prints this help message and quits

Switches:
    --from-dir DIRECTORY:str      Local directory containing a Dockerfile
    --from-url GIT_URL:str        Git repository URL containing a Dockerfile
    --sub-dir PATH:str            Sub-directory of git repo to use for the build

